Wayne McCurrie from FNB Wealth & Investments chose cash as his stock pick of the day and David Shapiro from Sasfin Securities chose L’Oreal. McCurrie said: “I’m going with cash, I’ve given up on SA Inc.” Shapiro said: “I’m going for beauty products, I’m going for L’Oreal. Clicks sell their product and if you look at their chart it’s very impressive.”